Benefit.description: One partner benefits more than the other

Mirror.description: Filled with interesting discussions and understanding

Identity.description: Interaction with a person of the same type

Activity.description: Active and enjoyable, but can tire both partners

Comparative.description: Relationships of mutual respect but potential misunderstanding

Semi-conflict.description: Tensions and disagreements, less intense than full conflict

Quasi-identity.description: Similar but not compatible, leading to misunderstandings

Kindred.description: Similar worldview but different focus, leading to respect with minor conflicts

Semi-dual.description: Very comfortable with slight differences for growth
